---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Word Hunt Solver"
  description="Learn how wordhuntsolvers.com collects, uses, and protects your data when you use our free word hunt solver tool."
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-10 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-700 dark:text-white sm:text-4xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 rounded-xl bg-accent-500/10 p-4 text-sm text-brand-600 dark:text-accent-300">
      Placeholder notice: replace the bracketed items below with your real analytics/ad setup before
      publishing, so this page matches your actual technical setup exactly.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      This Privacy Policy explains how wordhuntsolvers.com ("we", "our", "the site") collects and uses
      information when you use our word hunt solver and related tools. Effective date: [insert date].
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      This site does not currently use any other analytics or tracking scripts. We do use Google
      Search Console, which reports aggregate search performance data directly from Google, and does not
      place any cookies or scripts on this site. If you contact us through the Contact form or email, we
      collect the name, email, and message you provide.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      We use this information to understand how the tool is used, fix bugs, and improve accuracy. We do
      not sell your personal information.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Cookies and Other Services</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      This site does not currently set any analytics or advertising cookies. [Update this section if you
      add Google Analytics, ads, or any other outside script in the future, so it always matches what
      is actually running on the site.]
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Data Sharing and Third Parties</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      We do not share your personal data with third parties except as required by law or as needed to
      operate core site functions such as analytics.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      This site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information
      from children.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      Depending on your location, you may have the right to request access to, correction of, or deletion
      of your personal data. Contact us using the details on our Contact page to make a request.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Changes To This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2 class="mt-8 text-xl font-bold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">
      Questions about this policy? Reach out through our <a href="/contact" class="anchor-link">Contact Us</a> page.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
